name: Women's V-Neck: Get On My Level
description:
A 100% Cotton, Fashion Fit Tee.  Shirts are available in White, Black, & Grey in both Women's V-neck ($18) and Men's Crewneck($15). 

The tees are light weight for casual wearing and this design has the phrase "Get On My Level" with the En-de-yo brand sign-off +Nodaysoff.

The brand En-dē-yo is not a t-shirt company. It is a battle cry. It represents the revolution of our generation as we strive to fulfill our potential, which will ultimately bring us to 
a place of prominence.

Greatness is knowing what you want ... And working EVERYDAY to get it.  +Nodaysoff
